title: PREMIUM-Episode 27: Nagarjuna on Buddhist “Emptiness”
description: Primarily discussing "Reasoning: The Sixty Stanzas" and "Emptiness: The Seventy Stanzas," by the 2nd century Indian Buddhist Nagarjuna. With guest Erik Douglas.
